content: Teletilt Control System antennas are used to conduct radio frequency (RF) surveys.

description: File generated by ATC Lite, the software bundled with Teletilt Control System antennas (e.g., the ATC200-LITE-USB model); stores a report generated by the antenna and saves it in the Microsoft Word document format so that it can be opened with any Word-compatible software.
